Package BobcatLib.Subsystems.Elevators.Modules

Interface ElevatorIO

All Known Implementing Classes:
ElevatorReal
public interface ElevatorIO
Interface representing the Input/Output operations for an Elevator system. Provides methods for configuring, controlling, and monitoring the elevator's state.
